title: Prettyclicknepal

creator: Prettyclick
descriptionHtml:
We bring beauty lovers to a one-stop destination offering exclusive beauty brands, trends, and expertise. Prettyclick is all about celebrating beauty, and we share our customers’ love of empowering themselves with our products and expertise. Our brands includes Milani, Jordana,La Girl, 7th Heaven, Real Techniques, Tree Hut Shea, Dermacol, Orly.Cosmedica, and Skin Deva, better Skin co and more. Simply, we believe that every woman deserves the best. By encouraging our customers to EXPLORE, SWATCH, WATCH, and PLAY with beauty, we ensure that Prettyclick is a place to celebrate our love of beauty together.

OUR SPECIALTY
Prettyclick is an exclusive importer, distributor, and retailer for major American and European cosmetic and skincare brands in Nepal, and it remains the only Nepali business chain fully dedicated to beauty products. Because Nepal borders China, 70% of cosmetic products imported to Nepal are either counterfeit or bought from unreliable sources. Our success results from this. Prettyclick maintains high quality due to our commitment to refuse all counterfeit products, as nearly all of our products are purchased from the manufacturer or brand itself Available in all of Nepal’s major cities, Prettyclick remains the most trusted name in our budding beauty industry. We pride ourselves in being the fastest growing cosmetics company in Nepal, because our biggest asset is brand value.

We partner with beauty influencers and makeup artists, possess a large organic social media following, and hold makeup classes lead by experts, because Prettyclick is not just a brand—it’s a beauty movement. Since Prettyclick was established in 2012, we’ve held the belief that authentic products should not be a luxury, but a right.

We bring beauty lovers to a one-stop destination offering exclusive beauty brands, trends, and expertise. Prettyclick is all about celebrating beauty, and we share our customers’ love of empowering themselves with our products and expertise. Our brands includes Milani, Jordana,La Girl, 7th Heaven, Real Techniques, Tree Hut Shea, Dermacol, Orly.Cosmedica, and Skin Deva, better Skin co and more. Simply, we believe that every woman deserves the best. By encouraging our customers to EXPLORE, SWATCH, WATCH, and PLAY with beauty, we ensure that Prettyclick is a place to celebrate our love of beauty together.

OUR SPECIALTY
Prettyclick is an exclusive importer, distributor, and retailer for major American and European cosmetic and skincare brands in Nepal, and it remains the only Nepali business chain fully dedicated to beauty products. Because Nepal borders China, 70% of cosmetic products imported to Nepal are either counterfeit or bought from unreliable sources. Our success results from this. Prettyclick maintains high quality due to our commitment to refuse all counterfeit products, as nearly all of our products are purchased from the manufacturer or brand itself Available in all of Nepal’s major cities, Prettyclick remains the most trusted name in our budding beauty industry. We pride ourselves in being the fastest growing cosmetics company in Nepal, because our biggest asset is brand value.

We partner with beauty influencers and makeup artists, possess a large organic social media following, and hold makeup classes lead by experts, because Prettyclick is not just a brand—it’s a beauty movement. Since Prettyclick was established in 2012, we’ve held the belief that authentic products should not be a luxury, but a right.
descriptionShort: Makeup,skincare and all beauty related products

descriptionHtml:
At Prettyclick, we bring beauty enthusiasts to a one-stop destination, offering an exclusive array of beauty brands, the latest trends, and expert guidance. Our mission is to celebrate beauty and empower our customers with the carefully curated products and expertise we provide. With a selection of over 50 prestigious brands, our offerings span makeup, skincare, nail products, makeup accessories, personal care items, hair care essentials, and much more.

As Nepal’s most trusted name in beauty retail, Prettyclick has established more than 20 locations nationwide, where customers can enjoy an immersive in-store experience. We’re here to inspire confidence, empowering you to express your unique beauty.
